TITLE DefinitionRegistry2026v1
VERSION 1
CATEGORY GOVERNANCE

SUMMARY
Canonical registry particle for ALN definitions mirrored into SQL and Rust.

fields
  particlename    string   # HydrologicalBufferPhoenix2026v1
  category        string   # ECOSAFETY, HYDROLOGY, BIODIVERSITY, etc.
  primaryplane    string   # hydrologyMAR, biodiversity, carbon, energy, etc.
  role            string   # QPUDATASHARD, SUBSTRATE, CORRIDOR, GOVERNANCE
  lyapchannel     string   # hydraulics, materials, topology, dataquality, etc.
  alnfile         string   # repo-relative path to ALN file
  sqlfile         string   # repo-relative path to SQL mirror (optional)
  rustmodule      string   # Rust module path implementing mirror (optional)
  repotarget      string   # eco_restoration_shard, Eco-Fort, etc.
  shardprotocol   string   # EcoNetSchemaShard2026v1, PlaneWeightsShard2026v1, etc.
  versiontag      string   # 2026v1, 2026v2, etc.
  description     string   # short human-readable summary
  evidencehex     string   # hash over ALN+SQL+Rust bundle
  signingdid      string   # Bostrom DID of author
  created_utc     datetime # registration time
  updated_utc     datetime # last update
  active          bool     # true if definition is current

